HEADWORD: Sirkeer
<hw>Sir"keer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of several species of Asiatic cuckoos of the genus
<gen>Taccocua</gen>, as the Bengal <ex>sirkeer</ex> (<spn>Taccocua
sirkee</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sirloin</ent>⟦br⟧
